                "name": "War Stomp",
                "ability_type": "Supernatural",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Su",
                "text": "Rajput ambaris are trained to slam their skeletal front feet hard into the earth, creating a small shockwave that can knock nearby opponents prone. Any opponent standing immediately adjacent to a rajput ambari when it uses this ability must make a DC 25 Reflex save or be knocked prone. War stomp is a full-round action. The save DC is Strength-based."
